{"tid":2233640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反國歌法示威三男原分兩案 控方今申合併兼增襲警罪","createTime":"2020-10-07T09:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T09:37:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"95db53cef0280b3402c4f4afdaa11e30168d1572","tid":2233640,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"警方於今年5月28日反國歌法示威中拘捕逾300人，當中三名男子被控堵路、非法集結及襲警等罪，分兩案起訴。案件今在九龍城裁判法院再訊時，控方申請合併兩案，並針對兩名被告新增一項襲警罪。主任裁判官嚴舜儀應辯方要求，將案件押後至12月2日答辯，其間批准三人繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/KZBDTK3AINFRZIYSLFWE6WOS34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FKZBDTK3AINFRZIYSLFWE6WOS34%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=f844f5ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FKZBDTK3AINFRZIYSLFWE6WOS34%2F&h=4ac0def9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/KZBDTK3AINFRZIYSLFWE6WOS34/</a>"},{"pid":"f0c2e87a7c9bd76dc8febc79770492ab7a34c617","tid":2233640,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}